Flow
-> /signup -user signup using email and phone, email used as username and phone number for otp verification -> Otp generated

-> /verify-otp - otp verification & user data (req.body) storing in db

->Redirected to login page

->/login -verifying entered credentials through middlewares.

->/profile -user profile view and managing.

          -->/profile/updateInfo -(post method)-User bio update
          -->/profile/profile-picture -(post method)-User profile update.
          -->/profile/:id -(get method)-User profile view.
          -->/profiile/privacy/:id -(post method)-User privacy updation

->/view-profile -Verifying current user is admin or not and checking if the profile is public or not through middlewar(authorizeViewProfile)
